            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間10日12:53，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.87點（或2.01%），暫報349.44點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+7.76%</li><li>近 1 月：+18.55%</li><li>近 3 月：+22.41%</li><li>近 6 月：+29.2%</li><li>今年以來：+24.01%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Flash模組概念領漲+4.24%。其中    立萬利(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3054:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3054\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3054-TW</a>)            上漲        9.94%            ;        廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)            上漲        8.56%            ;        宇瞻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)            上漲        6.47%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>藍寶石材料概念領漲+3.87%。其中    合晶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6182:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6182\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6182-TW</a>)            上漲        7.21%            ;        永光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\